xvm version
xvm usage
xvm help

xvm init
xvm which [<plugin>]
xvm status [local|global] [<plugin>]
xvm remove

xvm set   [local|global] <plugin> <version>|stable|latest
xvm unset [local|global] <plugin>

xvm show <plugin> [installed|available|stable|latest]
xvm pull <plugin> <version>|stable|latest
xvm drop <plugin> <version>|stable|latest

xvm show plugin [installed|available]
xvm pull plugin <name>
xvm drop plugin <name>

xvm edit plugin <name>
xvm push plugin <name>
